summary:
Lots of us have home assistants in our homes nowadays. They re very clever. You can get recipes, playmusic, control your lights, and so much more with just a simple voice command. But home assistants are just1 example of an amazing development in technology called artificial intelligence, or AI for short.

We ve all heard that phrase, and most people could probably give a basic explanation, but who really knowsexactly what it is? Thankfully, this course will give you the insight you need, by explaining exactly what AI isand how it can be useful day to day.
